@@ -579,8 +579,9 @@ EOF
 	else
 		IBM_ARCH=powerpc
 	fi
-	if [ -x /usr/bin/oslevel ] ; then
-		IBM_REV=`/usr/bin/oslevel`
+	if [ -x /usr/bin/lslpp ] ; then
+		IBM_REV=`/usr/bin/lslpp -Lqc bos.rte.libc |
+			   awk -F: '{ print $3 }' | sed s/[0-9]*$/0/`
 	else
 		IBM_REV=${UNAME_VERSION}.${UNAME_RELEASE}
 	fi
